headline: Leading With Heart: Gen Expands Global Giving and Volunteering
summary: More than two-thirds of Gen employees volunteered last year, logging 8,300 hours. With our new grants program, teams are turning local passion into global impact - from building safe classrooms in Malaysia to mentoring future cyber leaders in Europe. ...
